Section 4: Coding Tasks

Example 4.1

User

Write a Python function to find the longest word in a string.
AI Response
def longest_word(s):
words = s.split()
return max(words, key=len) if words else ""

print(longest_word("The quick brown fox")) # "quick"

Example 4.2

User

Write a minimal Flask REST API.
AI Response
from flask import Flask, jsonify
app = Flask(__name__)

users = [{"id":1,"name":"Alice"},{"id":2,"name":"Bob"}]

@app.route("/users")
def get_users(): return jsonify(users)

if __name__ == "__main__": app.run(debug=True)

